    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Priced at $33,900, this vehicle is in good overall condition and should make a solid choice for someone looking for a well-kept car. It runs and drives well, the interior is clean and presentable, and the exterior shows nicely overall with typical signs of normal use for its age. It is not a mint showpiece, but it has clearly been cared for and still presents very well. Buyers can expect a dependable, good-condition vehicle that is ready to be enjoyed.",
