    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Rough, honest poor-condition example being sold as-is and priced accordingly. This car shows heavy age and wear throughout, with noticeable cosmetic flaws to the exterior, a tired interior, and the likelihood that it will need meaningful mechanical sorting and deferred maintenance addressed before being considered a dependable driver. It may suit someone looking for a budget project, restoration candidate, or parts car, but buyers should expect shortcomings and plan on repairs. Please come with realistic expectations\u2014this is not a clean turnkey car, but it is represented honestly for what it is.",
      "price": 4900.0,
