      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly ride with plenty of life and potential left? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts conversations for all the right reasons: affordable entry point, usable as-is for the right buyer, and a great option for someone handy or wanting a project they can make their own. If you appreciate a car with character and don\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC, this could be a smart buy without spending a fortune. Priced to sell and ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or budget driver with strong mechanical character and good bones. The powertrain pulls well, steering feels direct, and it has the kind of straightforward, serviceable setup enthusiasts appreciate. Cosmetically it shows age and will want attention, but it remains a compelling platform for someone who values usability, mechanical simplicity, and upside. Priced to move and well suited for a weekend refresh, parts donor, or inexpensive daily with personality.",
      "price": 5900.0,
